<br>
From a DPS point of view how should my weapons be put into my hands, and what should I be looking for to upgrade weapons.  <br>
<br>
I have seen the following rules and get a bit confused as they are somewhat mutually exclusive.<br>
<br>
Fastest weapon in off hand.<br>
Weapon with proc in primary hand.<br>
Weapon with highest weapon skill in primary hand.<br>
Having the same weapon in both hands is bad. <br>
Having weapons with the the same delay in both hands is bad.<br>
Highest damage weapon in primary hand.<br>
Highest ratio weapon in primary hand.<br>
<br>
