Why Fastest Weapon primary handed? To make the most of the damage bonus per swing.<br>
Why the best ratio weapon offhanded? To make the most of the DW check per swing.<br>
<br>
Procs are Procs. If it's beneficial to you ( i.e soloing a snare whip or kunzar ku'juch to keep mobs from running ) than primary handing that weapon is best for you until you get your proc off than swap bac to your optimum DPS setup.<br>
